27 January 2020 Members of the media are invited to a photo-opportunity and short remarks by the Minister in the Presidency, Jackson Mthembu on Wednesday, 29 January 2020, the first day of the Cabinet Lekgotla. Journalists wishing to cover the photo-opportunity and remarks are requested to submit their details before 13h00, Tuesday, 28 January 2020  to pheliswa@gcis.gov.za or matikweni@gcis.gov.za using the template below which must be completed in full. Name Surname ID/Passport Number Organisation Function Celluar number Email address                      The details of the photo-opportunity are as follows:Date: Wednesday, 29 January 2020Time: 09h30 (Journalists to arrive at 08h30)Venue: Sefako Makgatho Presidential Guest House, Pretoria NB: Access to the venue will only be granted to journalists who have submitted the required details.  Proof of identity as well as a Press Card or letter from the Editor confirming assignment will also be required. Enquiries:Phumla Williams, GCIS Acting Director-GeneralCell: 083 501 0139